seriesStmt.title: Gregor Joseph Werner: A thematic catalogue of his works

annot.p: Joseph Haydn compiled the introductions of the six oratorios Esther (WerW A.10), Absolon (WerW A.7), Holoferne (WerW A.6), Der verlohrene Sohn (WerW A.11), Adam (WerW A.13), and Job (WerW A.12) into this collection.
